    "Common mistakes include overcommitting to the board without follow-up, misusing Kozilek\u2019s Command\u2019s damage option when you need bounce, and failing to track opponent interaction.",
    "Remember that Glaring Fleshraker and Malevolent Rumble are identical in function, so prioritize casting them in response to threats to maximize value.",
    "Basking Broodscale\u2019s combo interaction is key\u2014practice trigger ordering to avoid unintended sacrifices."
